# text: And ultimately I feel that in the same way that we test flame-retardant pajamas in an inferno to ensure they wo n't catch fire when our child reaches across the stove , so these stories of families negotiating these extreme differences reflect on the universal experience of parenting , which is always that sometimes you look at your child and you think , where did you come from ?
